{"tid":1469340,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［令運動聚焦］而家應該FOCUS 818 遲啲再癱機場","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:23:39.000Z","uid":217816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"98f9808e1773b80c7a750017f9724ad08fbf3529","tid":1469340,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:28:45.000Z","msg":"好多人已經係咁話運動失焦<br />\n除左對家都針住黎話我地變質<br />\n自己人都開始會話唔知做緊咩 覺得有啲失焦<br />\n特別經過琴日之後<br />\n好明顯大家都已經因為太多突發事情 <br />\n未知點拆 同時太有情緒 <br />\n就有機會做左無咁好既決定<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">犯錯係可以接受<br />\n唔會割 唔會放棄<br />\n但一定要靜落黎檢討<br />\n一定要改善</span></span><br />\n<br />\n勇武既唔會因為你一時靜落黎之後勇唔到<br />\n你荒死政府唔再做衰野激起民憤咩？<br />\n反而和理非同跟得唔貼既人就會因為我地做既事整體觀感唔好而令佢地割蓆<br />\n<br />\n而家，真係真係應該冷靜落黎<br />\n今日再想癱機場的話都已經唔知咩方向同點入手<br />\n機場係有用 但個機場唔會走左去 <br />\n幾時都可以再黎<br />\n琴日癱得有效定無效大家有眼睇<br />\n咁點解唔暫時冷靜下<br />\n重整返陣戰？<br />\n呢幾日日日有大野 都已經無時間同空間比我地去討論同調整<br />\n雖然話無大台<br />\n但都唔等於唔洗討論<br />\n而家應該要冷靜 檢討再重新出發<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同時文宣818 <br />\nfocus叫人818出黎</span></span>"},{"pid":"f447b1433ffd7d7d5e70456381226583bf66eef6","tid":1469340,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:32:39.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f18f67a4bf16a4d0e67b84faea607271d33f9134","tid":1469340,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:32:49.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"09931b45bb4680858187bf9626ddd557a6fcf081","tid":1469340,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:33:01.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"93e4ae47ccb7ca3889aac8b5e7d210106d143ba3","tid":1469340,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:33:12.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"df6e2ca4574e559bbf1c442d20f64756a136b3ad","tid":1469340,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:34:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16fcab2dfbd706e1e7d47d508906379706ecf310","tid":1469340,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:23:27.000Z","msg":"Psuh"},{"pid":"a6099d0f5664c0889f076bb4f3491bdff1a37e47","tid":1469340,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:23:39.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}